text: avaru (musa) helidaru; ninu tolagibidu. I lokada badukinalli ninagiruva sikseyenendare ‘‘nannannu muttabedi’’ endu ninu, heluttirabeku. Ninagagi ondu samaya nigadiyagide. Adannu badalisalu ninnindagadu. Ninu astondu nistheyinda nambikondidda a ninna devarannom'me nodu. Naviga adannu suttu biduvevu mattu adara budiyannu nadiyalli harisibiduvevu
